            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>由著名的日系 RPG 游戏《女神异闻录 5》，故事是讲述在学生与偷心怪盗的双重生活下，让大人悔改的拯救剧情，其后并指出《皇家版》加强内容与及延伸作品《乱战》。而最近 Sega ATLUS 推出以策略战棋 RPG 为主要的《女神异闻录 5 战略版》。游戏不但有著全新的玩法，而且还是会保留「1MORE」、「总攻击」等战斗元素。游戏正式于 11 月 17 日正式发售，其中支援 Xbox Series X|S 及 One、PlayStation 4 / 5、Nintendo Switch 以及 PC 平台，并在首日加入 Xbox Game Pass。</p><p><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206462 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲全新游戏类型</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206471" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-32-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-32-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-32-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-32.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲风格延续前作</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206478" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-17-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-17-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-17-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-17.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲新角色登场</p><h2><span class="s1">故事加插在旧作，游玩前重温免疑惑</span></h2><p class="p1"><span class="s1">以《女神异闻录 5 战略版》故事的时间线，是在《皇家版》中后期之间，如果玩家没有游玩此系列的作品，会难免对于游戏的世界观感到疑惑。而且游戏中有著很大量的剧透与及后期内容，游戏也没有介绍角色与及游戏的世界观，新加入的玩家很难会代入进去游戏里，相反可能因为很多事情看不懂而会放弃。相对有认识的玩家，一定会对于《女 5》的角色重新再出现而感到兴奋，游戏还是巧妙地将每个角色的定位带出来。</span></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206465 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-10-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-10-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-10-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-10.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲曾经出现的角色</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206466" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲许多日常回忆对话</p><h2><span class="s1">可爱化的人物，但保留系列风格</span></h2><p class="p1"><span class="s1">虽然人物全部都被可爱化了，变得更 Q 版及偏向儿童向，不过只要游玩下去就会发觉没有太大不同。而且不管从人物上，或是从游戏界面上，都充满著《女 5》的风格，绝对能让玩家重新再爱上这风格。而游戏的剧情非常幽默，如果喜欢看剧情的玩家一定会被里面的对话会心一笑，游戏并不是单一只有文字对话。过场时有著不同的影片让玩家大呼过瘾，而且也是相当多影片让玩家慢慢欣赏，务求让玩家在《女神异闻录 5 战略版》不会感到无聊。</span></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206463 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有趣人物表情</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206481" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-18-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-18-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-18-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-18.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲介面保留原作风格</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206479" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-22-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-22-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-22-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-22.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可爱而不失霸气的角色</p><h2><span class="s1">循序渐进的游戏方式，让战斗慢慢刺激</span></h2><p class="p1"><span class="s1">在《女神异闻录 5 战略版》的游玩方式其实与《Mario + Rabbit》系列极为相似，当我以为每个游戏章节会比较简单与及不需要太多的操作，结果这次游戏给我非常深刻的印象。游戏随着进度慢慢让玩家了解更多游戏系统，例如有着击倒功能、「1more」功能、属性功能等等，甚至可以利用特定条件使出合力攻击，让玩家有更多发挥空间有着更多的可玩性及策略性。虽然元素上没有相克效果，不过有着不同的位移或附加伤害，这可以让玩家有更多有趣的组合去应付适人。</span></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206467 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-7-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-7-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-7-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-7.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲负面属性附加</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206468" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-14-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-14-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-14-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-14.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲共同总攻击</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206480" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-29-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-29-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-29-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-29.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲依旧可运用地形</p><h2><span class="s1">约 100 个人格面具合成</span></h2><p class="p1"><span class="s1">随着玩家完成游戏，会获得金色齿轮为奖励，而金色齿轮则代表着不同的人格面具，只要与不同的人格面具进行合成就有机会获得新的人格面具。而当中合成可以选择继承过往的技能，如果想沿用旧技能就必须从该技能的人格面具着手再合成上去。而当中超过 100 个面具等着玩家去合成，当然等级越高就代表可以加成角色的能力值就越高。除此之外玩家亦可以选择购买过往曾经合成的人格面具，用咗方便可以分岐更多新人格面具。</span></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206470 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-30-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-30-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-30-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-30.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲多款人格面具</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206477" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-21-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-21-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-21-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-21.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲合成后可选择继承技能</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206476" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-20-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-20-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-20-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-20.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可通过商店购买人格面具</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206469" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-31-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-31-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-31-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-31.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲合成新的人格面具</p><h2><span class="s1">团队等级减轻重刷，但影响深远</span></h2><p class="p1"><span class="s1">这次游戏是采用团队等级来代替角色个人等级，不过团队等级的用途非常广泛，首先会随着等级提升近战伤害。而当中人格面具也要按团队等级来合成，不能合成超过团队等级的人格面具。当然每个任务都会有不同条件让玩家达成，达成越多经验就越多，玩家可以先轻松玩然后重复游玩该任务来达成条件。没有角色等级之下玩家只能透过日常对话或支线任务来获得更多 GP，GP 可以在角色技能树上强化，从而获得更好的能力与状态。</span></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206464 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-28-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-28-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-28-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-28.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲日常对话有机会获得 GP</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206484" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-23-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-23-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-23-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-23.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲支线任务大大影响角色成长度</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206482" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-25-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-25-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-25-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-25.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲获得大量 GP</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206483" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-27-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-27-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-27-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-27.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲各角色技能树大同小异</p><h2><span class="s1">总结：保留《女神异闻录 5》风格的优良作品</span></h2><p class="p1"><span class="s1">比起正传作品，《女神异闻录 5 战略版》相对较为轻松以及画风较为 Q 版而更容易深受玩家喜爱。虽然游戏内容较为少，不过从游戏性，系统设计，甚至在背景音乐上也看到制作的用心，足以证明没有毁掉《女神异闻录 5》的招牌。而且一贯保留丰富的剧情内容，以及爽快的游戏流程，即使换上战棋游戏能让玩家融入其中。不管如何，在将近 50 游戏小时过程中，能够游玩《女神异闻录 5》新作品，结论是非常值得花时间来推荐大家游玩这个游戏！</span></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206473 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-5-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-5-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-5-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-5.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲角色聚首一堂</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206474" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可选择困难度</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206475" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-13-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-13-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-13-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-13.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲爽快又具战略性的游戏</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206472" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-26-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-26-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-26-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-26.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲特典送的，很无敌</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

