            <title>抖音母公司宣布裁员，结束子公司「朝夕光年」撤离游戏市场</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/28/bytedance-shut-down-nuverse-and-quit-from-gaming-marketing/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=bytedance-shut-down-nuverse-and-quit-from-gaming-marketing</link>
